04:44.500 --> 04:46.610
I... I somehow got suckered into letting her

04:46.640 --> 04:48.960
campaign with me all weekend.
I mean, i... it could be fun,

04:49.000 --> 04:50.350
-  right?
- I'm sor... mom,

04:50.380 --> 04:53.850
the most vocal bleeding-heart
