15:19.650 --> 15:21.330
- You had too much wine.
- Kitty, listen...

15:21.810 --> 15:24.380
It wasn't just the jet plane.

15:24.550 --> 15:26.790
The... they... they
started in about your wig.

15:26.830 --> 15:29.760
They said you spent thousands
and thousands of dollars

15:29.780 --> 15:32.440
