20:09.660 --> 20:10.630
How was the drive?

20:11.280 --> 20:12.970
- Oh, it wasn't bad.
- Whatever you do, don't go in the kitchen.

20:13.010 --> 20:15.200
Everybody's freaking out.
I'm gonna grab a sweater.

20:15.230 --> 20:16.190
You want one, Justin?

20:17.020 --> 20:20.280
- Justin.
- No, I would've asked. Thank you, Rebecca.

20:22.080 --> 20:22.920
Are you guys okay?

20:22.960 --> 20:25.160
We've been better. What about you?

20:25.200 --> 20:27.150
- How you feeling?
- I feel fine.

20:27.190 --> 20:29.200
What do they have you
taking these days? Taking?

20:29.240 --> 20:31.520
- For your heart, Robert.
- Atorva,

20:31.560 --> 20:33.860
which is why I'm gonna
have some more of this.

20:35.710 --> 20:36.530
Hi, guys.

20:36.560 --> 20:39.370
- How were the crowds?
- The crowds were large, friendly.

20:39.420 --> 20:43.070
Well... loud, excruciatingly loud.

20:43.430 --> 20:45.010
- Robert, can I talk to you for a minute?
- Sure.

20:46.680 --> 20:49.170
- Oh, don't go in the kitchen. Saul might kill you.
- What?

20:49.330 --> 20:51.730
That's nice. Oh, look
