22:21.220 --> 22:22.380
I'm sure it's fine.

22:22.600 --> 22:23.630
How's everyone doing in here?

22:23.680 --> 22:25.290
Oh, great. She's a little jittery.

22:25.340 --> 22:27.310
Kevin, drop it. He didn't
sleep well last night.

22:27.370 --> 22:29.070
- It's our fault.
