23:06.660 --> 23:08.680
I took the test this morning.

23:09.850 --> 23:12.340
- Well, that's a good thing, right?
- It's great for people like you,

23:12.360 --> 23:13.670
because it's spring cleaning for you.

23:13.720 --> 23:15.840
Isn't that what you
said, you go every year?

23:16.210 --> 23:18.420
But you see, I never opened that closet.

23:19.420 --> 23:21.410
Regardless of the world
that you grew up in,

23:21.450 --> 23:23.430
the world that I knew
was a lot less accepting.

23:24.710 --> 23:26.250
People died.

23:28.290 --> 23:29.520
Don't you get it?

23:30.030 --> 23:31.520
For me, bad news is po...

23:33.220 --> 23:34.470
so why don't you plate up this food?

23:34.520 --> 23:35.860
And I will get some fresh air.

23:39.090 --> 23:41.470
It's just pushing my buttons is all.

23:42.290 --> 23:44.180
It's just making me doubt everything.

23:45.320 --> 23:46.250
What are you doubting?

23:47.200 --> 23:49.810
Well, it's been two
months since my last test.

23:50.010 --> 23:51.150
And you were fine.

23:52.020 --> 23:53.680
But I have to have
another one in six months

23:53.720 --> 23:54.850
and another one after that.

23:54.890 --> 23:56.080
It's always gonna be there.

23:56.720 --> 23:58.230
You're not gonna get sick again.

24:00.150 --> 24:00.990
What if I do?

24:04.150 --> 24:05.180
What if I really...

