Don't do this. Don't.

24:10.020 --> 24:12.800
Don't let one person do this to you.

24:13.170 --> 24:15.300
You are up in the polls,
and you had a bad day.

24:16.010 --> 24:19.010
Okay, I am gonna go get us some wine.

24:28.540 --> 24:29.710
Where the hell is he going?

24:29.770 --> 24:31.800
You know, I don't know.
