24:31.860 --> 24:33.170
You know, I'm gonna go talk to him.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.420
Mom, stop. Don't.

24:34.630 --> 24:36.750
Don't get involved.

24:37.160 --> 24:37.700
Keep drinking.

24:37.750 --> 24:39.540
Yeah, you know, I'll
go to the kitchen, mom.

24:39.590 --> 24:40.920
I will find out what's going on, okay?

24:40.960 --> 24:42.760
I'll come with you for moral support.

24:44.330 --> 24:46.050
