- Oh, my gosh.

36:58.150 --> 36:59.940
That wedding I planned was so beautiful.

37:00.390 --> 37:03.580
Or I don't know, maybe David
and I will get married there.

37:03.620 --> 37:05.100
No, no, no, hold on, hold on.

37:05.540 --> 37:07.930
Our mothers want to throw
us that wedding in Hawaii

37:07.960 --> 37:09.570
