it. What do you think?

37:09.620 --> 37:12.860
Um, tell 'em thank you, but,
uh, no. Not Hawaii again.

37:12.900 --> 37:13.960
I'll tell them we'll think about it.

37:13.990 --> 37:16.270
Mom, we're gonna think about it. Hello?

37:17.830 --> 37:18.640
I lost her.

37:19.510 --> 37:21.820
Look, I just say, we
leave well enough alone.

37:21.860 --> 37:23.620
You know, every time we think
about having a big wedding,

37:23.660 --> 37:25.250
- something bad happens.
- I know,

37:25.310 --> 37:26.740
plus it's redundant.
We're already married.

37:26.770 --> 37:28.310
We should just let mom and dad do it.

37:28.311 --> 37:29.780
I mean, I'd go that way.

37:32.510 --> 37:33.940
Are you tired? You want me d drive?

37:34.020 --> 37:36.110
No. No, no, I'm fine. I'm fine.

37:36.870 --> 37:38.250
Why don't you find something on the radio?

37:46.560 --> 37:47.590
Oh, my God.

38:01.090 --> 38:02.150
Are you okay?

38:02.870 --> 38:03.880
Oh, God.

38:14.670 --> 38:16.120
- Scotty!
- Oh, my God. Kevin!

38:16.350 --> 38:17.360
Scotty, Scotty, are you okay?

38:18.290 --> 38:19.460
- I'm fine. I'm fine.
- Justin!

38:19.980 --> 38:22.000
I'm fine. I'm fine. Kevin,
are you okay? Are you hurt?

38:22.080 --> 38:23.830
- Help the others. Help the others.
- Mom... what?

