- Are you okay?
- I think we hit Robert's car.

38:46.820 --> 38:48.440
Oh, my God. There was a... there was a truck...

38:48.490 --> 38:50.160
- Where's my mom?
- This guy cut him off.

38:50.210 --> 38:52.090
Holly's in the car. I can't
get Holly out of the car.

38:52.360 --> 38:54.910
- Holly's hurt.
- Mom! Mom!

39:00.480 --> 39:02.570
- Just sit down over here.
- Call emergency.

39:02.610 --> 39:04.720
- Just sit down, all right? Just sit... 
