39:05.890 --> 39:07.100
I don't know!

39:10.470 --> 39:11.380
I see him.

39:15.260 --> 39:16.180
Saul!

39:16.390 --> 39:18.300
I'm fine. Are you okay?

39:18.380 --> 39:19.380
Yeah. Good. I'm...

39:19.420 --> 39:20.290
Don't touch me!

39:22.850 --> 39:23.870
You can't.

39:30.950 --> 39:32.570
Kitty! It's all right, Robert.

39:32.900 --> 39:34.060
- Kitty! Kitty!
- Oh, no, no.

39:34.110 --> 39:36.070
Justin, Justin. I think he's really hurt.

39:36.120 --> 39:37.950
Okay, okay. I think he's really hurt.

39:37.980 --> 39:40.230
- All right. Let me in. Let me in. Okay.
