39:40.290 --> 39:42.320
Hey, Robert. Hey, the... there's my man.

39:42.400 --> 39:44.470
Justin, help! Mom's bad.

39:46.220 --> 39:47.060
Justin...

39:47.760 --> 39:49.030
I'll wait for the ambulance.

39:50.080 --> 39:52.000
Go. All right, Kitty. Keep talking to him.

39:52.050 --> 39:53.880
Oh! I'll be back. I'll
be back, Robert. Okay?

39:55.710 --> 39:57.000
Oh, God.

39:58.170 --> 40:01.220
Holly. Rebecca, clear out. Clear. Rebecca.

40:01.300 --> 40:02.560
Holly? Holly, can you hear me?
I don't know if she's breathing.

40:02.570 --> 40:05.400
Can you hear me, Holly? Holly.

40:06.280 --> 40:08.920
Holly? Oh, good, good. Okay,
Holly, it's Justin, all right?

40:09.250 --> 40:12.460
I'm just gonna put this
on to keep you warm, okay?

40:12.660 --> 40:14.300
You're gonna be okay. She's gonna be okay.

40:15.530 --> 40:17.800
Okay, Robert, everything's
gonna be okay, honey.

40:17.960 --> 40:19.620
You're gonna be fine, okay? Talk to me.

40:19.980 --> 40:22.630
- Just talk to me, darling. It's okay.
- You were right.

40:23.450 --> 40:24.280
I was right?

40:25.920 --> 40:28.810
When we brought Evan home from
the hospital, I was scared...

40:30.370 --> 40:33.170
That I wouldn't be able to keep up.

40:35.900 --> 40:37.870
But then I saw you holding him...

40:40.230 --> 40:41.640
So strong...

40:43.070 --> 40:44.330
and so loving.

40:47.170 --> 40:48.460
And I knew that...

40:49.540 --> 40:50.560
you would.

40:55.040 --> 40:56.160
I knew it.

40:58.510 --> 40:59.500
Robert.

41:01.370 --> 41:04.180
Robert. Robert. Talk... talk to me.

41:04.890 --> 41:06.480
Oh, God. Robert...

41:06.850 --> 41:09.220
stay with me, Robert. Right here. Robert.

41:11.020 --> 41:11.600
Oh, my...

41:12.520 --> 41:13.240
Robert?

41:13.460 --> 41:15.090
Oh, my God. Oh, my God. Somebody...

41:15.770 --> 41:16.860
Some... oh, Robert.

41:17.880 --> 41:20.190
Robert, please. Please. Please, Robert.

41:20.430 --> 41:23.520
Stay with me. Robert, stay with...

